Re: Federal Trade Commission Substitues NAICS Codes for SIC Codes on HSR
Forms

                     Attached is a memorandum, from Sullivan & Cromwell 
concerning the above subject. A summary is also included at the end of the 
text of this e-mail message.

                     The attached file is in Adobe Acrobat format.  We 
believe most PCs will already have an Acrobat viewer
